data.description: Rare find in Mint Hill ~ single story home on large end lot, convenient to downtown Mint Hill. Detached 785 SF Garage has limitless uses. NO HOA! This adorable home offers spacious rooms, a private courtyard style patio and a large open yard with above ground pool.  A privacy fence surrounds the yard.  Inside a spacious LRM welcomes you in. A gas line (propane) is available to add a gas stove ~ complete w/ mantel in place. Open to the Dining area w/ tile floors leading to kitchen.  A large laundry room is an ideal mud room or walk in pantry.  Access to the patio from kitchen/dining is ideal for backyard cookouts. A spacious primary BRM w/ two closets. An updated bathroom has shiplap and new flooring. A covered front porch provides additional outdoor space to relax. Convenient to 485 and just 12 miles to Uptown Charlotte (via Lawyers Road / Albemarle Road). Roof new in 2021!
